Willis Rushton (birth registered JulySeptember 1936) birth registered in Pontefract district, is a professional rugby league footballer of the 1960s, playing at club level for Wakefield Trinity, as a Centre, i.e. number 3 or 4.

== Genealogical information ==
Willis Rushton's marriage to Beryl R. Berry was registered during OctoberDecember 1957 in Pontefract district.

